thinking about the thyroid.

714
00:32:45.090 --> 00:32:47.880
thinking about TSH as your primary first step

715
00:32:47.880 --> 00:32:51.570
for any diagnosis, being vigilant about pregnancy.

716
00:32:51.570 --> 00:32:52.980
If you have a parathyroid question,

717
00:32:52.980 --> 00:32:56.010
it's most likely gonna be a hyper parathyroid state.

718
00:32:56.010 --> 00:32:58.770
If you have a pituitary mass, think about the type

719
00:32:58.770 --> 00:33:00.720
of hormone that's being affected.

